Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: We were quite busy building our way up on becoming a Zone in the Cosmos Network (Read more here: https://bit.ly/2SDwK21). So no, it's not another dead project, just a very busy one.  LATEST UPDATES: KUE Token is usable in the platform and you can deposit it directly from you ETH Wallet. We have implemented the Challenges Framework (web and mobile) and users have already started to Create and Participate in Challenges. We are participating in the Game-of-Stakes as a Cosmos Network Validator.  NEAR FUTURE PLANS: We are switching the current implementation of our Challenges from Ethereum to Kuende Blockchain. We are launching the platform in South Korea. KUE Token holders will be able to purchase from our market-place, the Kshop, exclusive goods/services and experiences such as a helicopter ride over the Grand Canyon, amazing trips to Kuala Lumpur, a parachute jump in the Caribbeans etc. An overview on our accomplishments thus far here: https://bit.ly/2TCF1TY  GREATEST NEWS:  KUE Token is listed on CoinBene Exchange. As one of the few ICOs that have raised more than 18,000 ETH and have an established product with an use for the Token in the platform, Kuende has been under exchangesâ€™ radar for quite some time now.  We are more than happy to find that CoinBene is seeing the potential that a blockchain fueled social media platform has and we fully support their decision to list us.  https://www.coinbene.com/#/notice/detail/2762

Author: Kuende
Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: Kuende is proud to announce that we have integrated the Bancor Protocol and the KUE Token has been added to the Bancor Network, a decentralized cross-chain liquidity network enabling instant conversions between 8700+ token pairs on EOS and Ethereum.  Kuendeâ€™s integration with Bancor provides a user-friendly, secure and fast way for cryptocurrency holders to get KUE Tokens using not only BTC or ETH, but more than 140 ERC20 and EOS tokens in the Bancor Network. Furthermore, KUE holders are gaining access to continuous liquidity regardless of trade volume or exchange listings.  The Bancor Network is offering the possibility to easily convert between KUE and more than 8700 token pairs in the network in a single action. The user experience of Bancor resembles that of Coinbase and other popular custodial wallets in that users can manage and convert between tokens on different blockchains in a slick, intuitive app. But behind the scenes, users of Bancor transact directly with smart contracts on the blockchain and remain in full control of their funds and private keys at all times.  Users can perform conversions directly from the Bancor Wallet or any Web3 Wallet, such as MetaMask or Trezor, or using Scatter on EOS. Conversions occur instantly and are processed fully on-chainâ€Šâ€”â€Šfrom pricing to executionâ€Šâ€”â€Šensuring maximum transparency and safety. Live tokens on the network include ERC20 tokens like DAI (Maker Dao), BNB (Binance) and BAT (Basic Attention Token), as well as EOS-based tokens like IQ (Everipedia), DICE (BetDice), BLACK (eosBLACK) & many more.   With KUE available in your Kuende Wallet you will be able to engage with the platform by staking your KUE to Create or Vote Challenges in order to win Kuende Points. Starting with the Beta Version of the Challenges you will be able to use both Tokens to purchase exclusive goods or services from our marketplace, the Kuende Shop.   Check our Product: www.kuende.com Follow us on Twitter Follow us on Medium  Chat on Telegram (English), Telegram (Turkish), Kakao (Korean) Visit ICO Website Contact Email: kuende@kuende.com

Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: Why Blockchain? Why Tendermint? Why Cosmos Network?    In the recent past weeks weâ€™ve been receiving a lot of â€œWhyâ€ questions, especially centered around our intersection with blockchain and the decisions around it. All of the questions are covered in our Whitepaper and surely all of them were answered multiple times within our community channels, such as Bitcointalk or Telegram. Nevertheless weâ€™ve concluded that our community needs a central point where all blockchain related questions are gathered and addressed.  This article should act both as a reference point for those who couldnâ€™t read through the entire Whitepaper and as a refresher for those that previously heard the answers. Therefore, in the rest of this article we are going to cover the following question:    - Why do you use/need blockchain?    - Why do you initially use Ethereum and an internal ledger?    - Why Tendermint & Cosmos Network?    Read the full article: https://medium.com/kuende/why-blockchain-why-tendermint-why-cosmos-network-a19d590a0d26

Author: Kuende
Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: Kuende Is A Gem For South Korea And Turkey    Kuende is the only blockchain based social media app that rewards users for engaging in real-life experiences. So, when a country's citizens make an entire website about it, you know you're onto something. Blockchain enthusiasts from South Korean are excited for Kuende, an up and coming social media app that uses a blockchain and cryptocurrency to engage its users in real life experiences. South Korea is one of the biggest hubs for cryptocurrency, with some reports showing that one in three South Korean workers have invested in at least one project. To take it one step further, South Koreans even developed their own cryptocurrency, and some of the largest exchanges in the entire world call this country their home.  Read the complete article: http://news.morningstar.com/all/access-wire/ASWAccesswire527796MSN/kuende-is-a-gem-for-south-korea-and-turkey.aspx

Author: Kuende
Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: Kuende Partners With The Most Fully Featured Bounty Platform - Bountyhive    Iâ€™m so excited to announce that Kuende is partnering with my favorite bounty platform, Bountyhive! Let me tell you something - when we were first mulling over the possibilities of our bounty program (which you can read about here), I realized that we didnâ€™t have a very good way to make sure people knew about it. Yes, there is Telegram, there is Medium, and there are forums. But itâ€™s hard to keep track of all of that. Even worse, itâ€™s hard for bounty hunters to have a centralized place to find the best bounties. Bountyhive changed all of this for us.  Bounty hunters that create hype are one of the most important parts of getting an ICO funded. From social media posts to influencer videos and everything in between, they are an integral marketing piece. Our bounty program was so innovative and out of the ordinary that we werenâ€™t entirely sure of how well it would perform. There are a lot of bounty programs that fall flat on their face because it doesnâ€™t get enough participants.  Weâ€™re partnering with Bountyhive because we want ICOs and blockchain-based projects to succeed. I really mean it! Blockchain and crypto businesses need to work together (yes, I will keep on repeating it because is the only way to accelerate the blockchain mass adoption). Kuende is providing a social space for these businesses to thrive, engage their customers, and provide their tokens as rewards. Bountyhive is very much doing the same, providing support for businesses still trying to raise funds.    Read the rest of the article here: https://medium.com/kuende/kuende-partners-with-the-most-fully-featured-bounty-platform-bountyhive-3f2f62e13fee

Body: Announcing Kuende Token Airdrop For IPSX Token Holders      As part of the partnership with IPSX, Kuende is offering a special Airdrop for all the IPSX token holders that contribute to Kuendeâ€™s Public Sale. Only the first 10,000 to register are eligible. The rules are as follows:  IPSX token holders register for the Kuende Whitelist to receive Kuende Tokens (KUE) When you are in the process of completing your KYC procedure, add the ETH wallet in which you have IPSX tokens as well (this is the same wallet in which you will receive the airdrop in KUE) After the ICO is over, Kuende will check all the addresses that contributed to the public sale that had IPSX tokens at the moment they have submitted their contribution All IPSX token holders that contribute to the public sale with a minimum of 1 ETH will receive an airdrop of 2,500 KUE. A contributor of 3 ETH or more will receive 10,000 KUE. Those who have contributed at least 6 ETH will receive 30,000 KUE. These are not cumulative (i.e. you wouldnâ€™t receive the 3 ETH and 6 ETH airdrops)  Read the rest on https://medium.com/kuende/announcing-kuende-token-airdrop-for-ipsx-token-holders-ddb9082b0002

Author: Kuende
Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: Thank you, Kardon!  Indeed, the space is very hard to penetrate. Fortunately, we re bringing a paradigm shift in terms of what people are used to when it comes to social media platforms: we're not focused on keeping users online as much as possible, but on getting them to interact in real life. With that being said and given the fact that humans are social creatures and offline interaction can't be compared with the shallow digital communication, we believe people will find it more than natural to become part of Kuende. It's a desire of being connected that lives in all of us; we're only suppressing by staying behind the screen because nobody is focused on providing us with context so that we interact offline (Except for night clubs, music festivals and similar - things that aren't available on a daily basis).

Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: Kuendeâ€Šâ€”â€ŠRebuilding the Human Social Connection (Part 2)    Last week, I spoke about how Kuende can help fix the social isolation issue that has become more and more common. This week, and to complete the article, I wanted to speak about a topic that I believe is even more pressingâ€Šâ€”â€Šthe effects of social media on our minds.  Mental health is a hot topic right now, and itâ€™s been entirely triggered by the intrusion of social media into every facet of our lives. Everywhere, experts are warning against addiction, body image issues, feelings of loneliness, and withdrawal. The truth is, people want to connect, otherwise social media wouldnâ€™t even exist. The problem is that social media is so easy to access and the dopamine hits are so effortless that users have become hooked. In many ways, they are slaves to their online personas, and this addiction separates them from meeting people offline, or, as we used to call it, â€œreal lifeâ€.  Read the entire article here: https://medium.com/kuende/kuende-rebuilding-the-human-social-connection-part-2-e0d6158b735e

Author: Pavel-Kuende
Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: We don't consider $17.8M to be a large amount for 2.5 years of development, marketing, research and acquisitions. We are already 24 in the team, with an immense backend infrastructure and our plan is to scale the team in the following 6-8 months to 100 members, 60-65% of them being developers. We are already building AI and will start the AR development next year as well.  So it may seem a big hard cap for a Dapp, but I feel like I have to underline the fact that our last investment was 2 years ago for an evaluation of $10M.  Thank you for your feedback

Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: New Partnership (Part 1) https://medium.com/kuende/new-partnership-part-1-aef25b35da34  We are excited to announce that we have formed a strategic partnership with OneQube to support us with marketing and strategy services. As part of our partnership, OneQube will provide marketing services for all phases of our ICO (pre and post) as well as hands-on marketing for the blockchain-based platform launch. OneQube is also assisting us in strategy guidance, regarding both the Kuende airdrop, bounty program, and public relation campaigns.  Choosing OneQube as a partner was an easy choice, as our companies are focused on engaging audiences while aiming to revolutionize the way we utilize social media. Using cutting edge technology, OneQube has the unique ability to target the crypto and blockchain audience using itâ€™s custom audiences, behavioral targeting, and modern competitive strategy methodology.  OneQube has previously assisted in marketing ventures for a number of ICO success cases, including Legolas Exchange, XTRD, and CanYa. Additionally, oneQube has added Varanidae and Arianne to itâ€™s portfolio this quarter.  Kuende believes it is exceedingly difficult to find a crypto-based marketing agency that can perform under the pressure of ever changing ad regulation. What sold us was OneQubeâ€™s focus on using technology and custom audiences to help propel great ideas forward on social media. This meant to us that they were ready to pivot their strategy with changing market conditions to meet our goals and KPIâ€™s. Along with assisting with Kuendeâ€™s ICO marketing and PR, oneQube will also develop long term and sustainable strategies for app user acquisition and large scale platform adoption.  Kuendeâ€™s community is growing rapidly, and we are excited to announce our bounty campaign will go live in mid-July. Our public sale is scheduled for late-August.

Title: ğŸ”µğŸ”µ[ANN][ICO CLOSED]Kuende - Creating real life experiencesğŸ”µğŸ”µ
Body: Yes, it is Swahili! It means Growth and Evolution  Also, Kuende is a boy name in Swahili, and describes a person very much inclined to give help and comfort to those in need. Kuende has a natural penchant for working with the old, the young, the sick, or the underprivileged. Although Kuende may have considerable creative and artistic talents, the chances are that Kuende will devote herself to an occupation that shows concern for the betterment of the community.The positive side of the number 6 suggests that Kuende is very loving, friendly, and appreciative of others. Kuende has a depth of understanding that produces much sympathetic, kindness, and generosity. The qualities of the 6 make the finest and most concerned parent and one often deeply involved in domestic activities. Openness and honesty is apparent in her approach to all relationships.
